title: Wall Street Breakfast August 4: Walmart Lays Off Corporate Employees After Guidance Cut
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Walmart lays off hundreds of corporate employees after guidance cut. Two senators unveil bill that would put bitcoin, ethereum within scope of CFTC. Tesla continues to climb premarket ahead of 'Cyber Roundup' event. Catch today’s WSB article here.
